</user_query>"}]},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how to modify the color of a button when it's disabled. Looking at the current code, I can see they have a Button composable with:

```kotlin
Button(
 onClick = onAddNote,
 colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(MaterialTheme.colorScheme.surface),
 enabled = title.isNotBlank() && content.isNotBlank(),
 shape = RoundedCornerShape(20.dp),
 modifier = Modifier.padding(start = 8.dp)
) {
 Text(
 text = "Save Note",
 color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onSurface,
 style = MaterialTheme.typography.labelLarge
 )
}
